            <div class="service-process-step">
                <div class="service-process-num">1</div>
                <h3>Flat 5.8% Income Tax</h3>
                <p>Idaho taxes retirement income at a flat 5.8% rate. This includes 401(k)/IRA withdrawals, pensions, and most other income. Strategic planning can help minimize this tax burden.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-process-step">
                <div class="service-process-num">2</div>
                <h3>No Estate or Inheritance Tax</h3>
                <p>Idaho does not impose estate or inheritance taxes, which simplifies legacy planning. This can be advantageous for wealth transfer strategies compared to many other states.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="service-process-step">
                <div class="service-process-num">3</div>
                <h3>Property Tax Planning</h3>
                <p>Idaho offers property tax relief programs for seniors, including the Circuit Breaker program. We help you understand and maximize available benefits.</p>
